snippet: Gunmen in Iraq seized and later released a prominent Sunni politician, officials said Saturday, as confusion remained over who abducted the lawmaker....

headline.print_headline: Sunni Politician Seized in Iraq Released by Gunmen
headline.main: Sunni Politician Seized in Iraq Released by Gunmen

lead_paragraph: Gunmen in Iraq seized and later released a prominent Sunni politician, officials said Saturday, as confusion remained over who abducted the lawmaker.
